snippet.title: Dartoster
snippet.description: In the midst of the war, you stumble upon the headquarters of opponents who have become zombies. Armed to the teeth, zombie soldiers want to kill you. There are many of them and they are very angry. Use your weapons to defeat enemies and change the course of the war. Good luck!
